# 11. The Simple Mental Model

```text
.venv/bin/python
= this project's Python

pip install
= installs packages into the Python you choose

pytest
= runs tests

TestClient
= fake browser/client for testing FastAPI routes

httpx
= request/response engine used by TestClient

requests
= real HTTP requests from your CLI to your running FastAPI server

uvicorn
= starts your FastAPI server
```

---

# 12. Most Important Rule to Remember

```text
Create .venv with python3.

After that, use .venv/bin/python for everything inside this project.
```

Good:

```bash
.venv/bin/python -m pip install requests
.venv/bin/python -m pip install pytest httpx
.venv/bin/python -m pytest
.venv/bin/python -m uvicorn app.main_api:app --reload
.venv/bin/python app/cli/cli.main.py
```

Avoid:

```bash
pip install requests
pytest
uvicorn app.main_api:app --reload
python app/cli/cli.main.py
```
